<i>♪ A little bit of Erica by my side ♪</i>

1005
00:51:43.976 --> 00:51:46.728
<i>♪ A little bit of Rita's all I need ♪</i>

1006
00:51:46.729 --> 00:51:49.439
<i>♪ A little bit of Tina's what I see ♪</i>

1007
00:51:49.440 --> 00:51:52.150
<i>♪ A little bit of Sandra in the sun ♪</i>

1008
00:51:52.151 --> 00:51:55.238
<i>♪ A little bit of Mary all night long ♪</i>

1009
00:51:56.239 --> 00:51:57.281
[Annie] <i>Well...</i>

1010
00:51:58.241 --> 00:52:01.743
That was the best stroganoff
I have ever had.

1011
00:52:01.744 --> 00:52:03.328
[Kathy] It definitely wasn't.

1012
00:52:03.329 --> 00:52:05.832
- but that's kind of you.
- [chuckles]

1013
00:52:08.209 --> 00:52:10.585
You have something you want to say?

1014
00:52:10.586 --> 00:52:11.796
Sorry.

1015
00:52:13.297 --> 00:52:14.632
You want to try that again?

1016
00:52:15.716 --> 00:52:17.217
[sighs] I'm sorry.

1017
00:52:17.218 --> 00:52:19.594
[Rick] Good.
But you're grounded till you're 20.

1018
00:52:19.595 --> 00:52:21.472
Mm. more like 30.

1019
00:52:22.557 --> 00:52:24.851
I hope we see each other again.

1020
00:52:25.935 --> 00:52:27.186
Me. too.

1021
00:52:34.443 --> 00:52:35.819
[Rick] Annie?

1022
00:52:35.820 --> 00:52:37.655
Don't make the same mistake I did.

1023
00:52:38.739 --> 00:52:41.741
Don't give up on the people you love.
all right?

1024
00:52:41.742 --> 00:52:43.493
[wistful music playing]

1025
00:52:43.494 --> 00:52:44.495
[chuckles softly]

1026
00:52:48.082 --> 00:52:49.500
[clears throat]

1027
00:52:59.343 --> 00:53:00.636
[sighs]

1028
00:53:03.139 --> 00:53:05.141
[gasping breaths]

1029
00:53:10.313 --> 00:53:12.315
[heavy thudding]

1030
00:53:18.070 --> 00:53:20.573
[tense. atmospheric music playing]

1031
00:53:21.657 --> 00:53:24.243
[groaning]

1032
00:53:28.831 --> 00:53:31.208
[breathing heavily]

1033
00:53:34.420 --> 00:53:36.088
[shouts]

1034
00:53:45.765 --> 00:53:47.767
[whirring]

1035
00:53:55.066 --> 00:53:56.817
The V1 wasn't here.

1036
00:54:04.992 --> 00:54:06.410
Were you...

1037
00:54:08.120 --> 00:54:09.246
Were you crying?

1038
00:54:12.875 --> 00:54:15.044
Just fucking do it already.

1039
00:54:15.795 --> 00:54:18.381
[somber music playing]

1040
00:54:36.148 --> 00:54:37.483
[gasps softly]

1041
00:54:41.112 --> 00:54:42.363
[door closes]

1042
00:54:48.577 --> 00:54:49.912
Thank you.

1043
00:54:50.705 --> 00:54:52.957
We wouldn't have made it out
if you hadn't stepped up.

1044
00:54:54.041 --> 00:54:57.503
Oh. Yeah. well. taking charge...

1045
00:54:58.754 --> 00:55:00.755
...was the most horrible thing
I've ever done.

1046
00:55:00.756 --> 00:55:03.134
Never let me do it again. Never.

1047
00:55:07.346 --> 00:55:09.598
I'm sorry I called you
a feckless junkie man-whore.

1048
00:55:10.683 --> 00:55:13.643
I don't remember you calling me that.

1049
00:55:13.644 --> 00:55:16.230
I didn't? I thought I did.

1050
00:55:17.314 --> 00:55:19.065
You're not wrong.

1051
00:55:19.066 --> 00:55:22.569
I was. once.

1052
00:55:22.570 --> 00:55:24.779
But I am clean now.

1053
00:55:24.780 --> 00:55:28.117
And I can be whatever you need.

1054
00:55:29.118 --> 00:55:31.746
[soft. atmospheric music playing]

1055
00:55:33.622 --> 00:55:35.458
I don't want to change you.

1056
00:55:36.876 --> 00:55:39.128
It's that...

1057
00:55:40.838 --> 00:55:43.174
...I'm trying to change myself.

1058
00:55:45.009 --> 00:55:46.885
The reason I can speak now. it's...

1059
00:55:46.886 --> 00:55:50.013
it's because I did so much work
to let go of my...

1060
00:55:50.014 --> 00:55:51.515
chaos.

1061
00:55:53.142 --> 00:55:54.310
The thing is...

1062
00:55:55.394 --> 00:55:56.895
...you love chaos.

1063
00:55:56.896 --> 00:55:58.396
You thrive in it.

1064
00:55:58.397 --> 00:55:59.607
Which is fine. but...

1065
00:56:01.192 --> 00:56:03.110
...I can't go back to that.

1066
00:56:07.990 --> 00:56:10.034
So. where does that leave us?

1067
00:56:19.627 --> 00:56:21.044
[groans]

1068
00:56:21.045 --> 00:56:23.004
- [whirring]
- [electrical buzzing]

1069
00:56:23.005 --> 00:56:24.173
[loud thud]

1070
00:56:38.395 --> 00:56:39.938
I'm sorry.

1071
00:56:39.939 --> 00:56:41.648
I shouldn't have left you.
I should've been here.

1072
00:56:41.649 --> 00:56:45.151
Actually. I'm so. so glad you weren't.

1073
00:56:45.152 --> 00:56:46.320
Super good day to miss.

1074
00:56:49.281 --> 00:56:51.658
- [speaks Russian over video]
- [device clicking over video]

1075
00:56:51.659 --> 00:56:53.743
[clears throat over video]

1076
00:56:53.744 --> 00:56:55.746
[Russian chatter continues over video]

1077
00:57:00.960 --> 00:57:02.086
[Butcher] Listen. mate.

1078
00:57:02.670 --> 00:57:04.963
- That shite I said...
- Hey.

1079
00:57:04.964 --> 00:57:06.714
Don't tell me you didn't mean it. a'ight?

1080
00:57:06.715 --> 00:57:09.634
'Cause I sure as hell meant
every fucking word I said.

1081
00:57:09.635 --> 00:57:11.262
So. we got a problem?

1082
00:57:16.225 --> 00:57:17.892
[chuckles]

1083
00:57:17.893 --> 00:57:19.102
We cool. man.

1084
00:57:19.103 --> 00:57:20.437
We cool.

1085
00:57:28.070 --> 00:57:29.529
What are you doing?

1086
00:57:29.530 --> 00:57:31.072
Just thinking.

1087
00:57:31.073 --> 00:57:34.409
Well. the shit show is on.

1088
00:57:34.410 --> 00:57:35.493
[button clicks]

1089
00:57:35.494 --> 00:57:37.537
[singer over video] <i>♪ From sea ♪</i>

1090
00:57:37.538 --> 00:57:41.583
{\an8}<i>♪ to shining ♪</i>

1091
00:57:41.584 --> 00:57:44.502
{\an8}[full choir] <i>♪ sea ♪</i>

1092
00:57:44.503 --> 00:57:48.214
<i>♪ America ♪</i>

1093
00:57:48.215 --> 00:57:51.218
- [cheering and applause]
- Yes! Yes!

1094
00:57:55.514 --> 00:57:57.056
Brothers and sisters.

1095
00:57:57.057 --> 00:57:58.850
[cheering]

1096
00:57:58.851 --> 00:58:02.312
Brothers and sisters.
we are truly. truly fortunate

1097
00:58:02.313 --> 00:58:04.189
to bear witness on this day.

1098
00:58:04.190 --> 00:58:07.108
- [congregation murmuring]
- Because today...

1099
00:58:07.109 --> 00:58:09.944
is the greatest day
in the history of Samaritan's Embrace.

1100
00:58:09.945 --> 00:58:12.448
- Can I get an amen?
- [congregation] Amen!

1101
00:58:13.449 --> 00:58:16.034
I mean. I love all this. love.

1102
00:58:16.035 --> 00:58:18.411
but don't you believe in Jesus
or whatever?

1103
00:58:18.412 --> 00:58:20.246
I did.

1104
00:58:20.247 --> 00:58:21.664
Now I believe in Homelander.

1105
00:58:21.665 --> 00:58:23.416
- [Bashley] <i>She's lying.</i>
- No shit.

1106
00:58:23.417 --> 00:58:25.543
- Excuse me?
- [laughs softly]

1107
00:58:25.544 --> 00:58:27.170
[congregation murmuring]

1108
00:58:27.171 --> 00:58:30.048
But today. brothers and sisters. today.

1109
00:58:30.049 --> 00:58:33.259
we set America back on its true course.

1110
00:58:33.260 --> 00:58:34.928
[cheering and applause]

1111
00:58:34.929 --> 00:58:37.180
Starting today. brothers and sisters.

1112
00:58:37.181 --> 00:58:42.685
we commit ourselves
to a divine rebranding.

1113
00:58:42.686 --> 00:58:46.522
We will be patriots of faith.

1114
00:58:46.523 --> 00:58:50.610
We will fulfill
our Founding Fathers' dream.

1115
00:58:50.611 --> 00:58:55.573
Today. starting today.
Samaritan's Embrace becomes

1116
00:58:55.574 --> 00:58:58.910
the Democratic Church of America.

1117
00:58:58.911 --> 00:59:01.747
[cheering and applause]

1118
00:59:02.957 --> 00:59:07.043
And here. to share his holy plan
for our new church.

1119
00:59:07.044 --> 00:59:09.003
he is not just a man...

1120
00:59:09.004 --> 00:59:11.172
[congregation murmuring]

1121
00:59:11.173 --> 00:59:14.593
...he's not just a super man...

1122
00:59:18.889 --> 00:59:24.227
...he is the Prophet of the Lord!

1123
00:59:24.228 --> 00:59:26.187
[applause]

1124
00:59:26.188 --> 00:59:30.191
He is the Prophet of America!

1125
00:59:30.192 --> 00:59:33.946
He is the Prophet Homelander!

1126
00:59:35.614 --> 00:59:38.158
[cheering]

1127
00:59:51.005 --> 00:59:54.465
[congregation chanting] Homelander!
Homelander! Homelander!

1128
00:59:54.466 --> 00:59:56.260
Homelander! Home--

1129
01:00:01.307 --> 01:00:02.474
[gasps]

1130
01:00:04.393 --> 01:00:07.980
[church organ playing
"America the Beautiful"]

1131
01:00:34.048 --> 01:00:36.050
♪ ♪

1132
